  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Industrial Waste Manipulation Device",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "工业废料处理装置",
    "TraditionalChinese": "工業廢棄物操控裝置"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "This remarkable technology transforms the Multi-Tool into a powerful kinetic manipulator, capable of attracting and repelling industrial waste via a localized magnetic field.<br><br>Access the Gravitino Coil by pressing <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span>, and attract industrial waste with <span class=\"name name-img\">ALTATTACK</span>. Magnetized objects can be launched from the Coil with <span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span>, or gently released with <span class=\"name name-img\">ALTATTACK</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "这项卓越的技术将多用途工具转变为强大的动能操纵器，能够通过局部磁场吸引和排斥工业废料。<br><br>按下<span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span>即可进入引力微子线圈，并使用<span class=\"name name-img\">ALTATTACK</span>吸引工业废料。磁性物体可使用<span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span>从线圈中发射出去，或使用<span class=\"name name-img\">ALTATTACK</span>来轻轻释放。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "這項卓越的科技將工具組轉化為強大的動力操控器，能夠透過局部磁場吸引或排斥工業廢棄物。<br><br>按下 <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span> 即可開啟伴重力子線圈，然後使用 <span class=\"name name-img\">ALTATTACK</span> 吸引工業廢棄物。磁性物體可使用 <span class=\"name name-img\">ATTACK</span> 從線圈中發射，或使用 <span class=\"name name-img\">ALTATTACK</span> 輕輕放開。"
  },
